        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " function is a numeric data type that matches the data type of the input parameters. If the input parameters are of different numeric types, the function should handle type conversion to ensure consistent comparison and return the appropriate numeric type that can accommodate the smallest value."
        }
